OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782240488
OL,3,CFarage defends #5 million gift saying
OL,4,C'no one cares', as investigation
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FNigel Farage doubled down on defending
OL,8,Fthe undeclared gift he received from a
OL,9,Fcrypto businessman
OL,11,FNigel Farage has said that "no one
OL,12,Fcares" about the ongoing investigation
OL,13,Finto an undeclared #5 million gift
OL,14,Ffrom a Thailand-based crypto
OL,15,Fbusinessman.
OL,17,FThe Reform UK leader has repeatedly
OL,18,Fdenied wrongdoing over the gift from
OL,19,FChristopher Harborne, a major party
OL,20,Fdonor, insisting it was unconnected to
OL,21,Fhis political activity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
