FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782240488
OL,3,CFarage defends #5 million gift saying
OL,4,C'no one cares', as investigation
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FHe doubled down on this defence in his
OL,8,Finterview with ITV's Good Morning
OL,9,FBritain on Tuesday, insisting the
OL,10,Fmoney is a gift, "it's not a donation"
OL,11,Fand that he doesn't believe he's
OL,12,F"broken any rules".
OL,14,FFarage repeated his previous claims
OL,15,Fthat the money was given for him to
OL,16,Fhave security and protection, saying
OL,17,F"the state has consistently refused to
OL,18,Fprovide me with any protection at all"
OL,19,Fdespite his claims of being the most
OL,20,Fphysically attacked politician in the
OL,21,Fcountry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
