OL,3,CFarage defends #5 million gift saying
OL,4,C'no one cares', as investigation
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FDespite this, on Tuesday morning, he
OL,13,Fsaid that he had not actually "spent a
OL,14,Fpenny" and told GMB that it was an
OL,15,F"unconditional" gift and could be
OL,16,Fspent on anything, even suggesting he
OL,17,F"can spend it on cars".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
