PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782240488
OL,3,CFarage defends #5 million gift saying
OL,4,C'no one cares', as investigation
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FParliament's standards commissioner,
OL,8,FDaniel Greenberg, has opened an
OL,9,Finvestigation into Mr Farage over the
OL,10,Fgift and whether the Clacton MP should
OL,11,Fhave declared it in his register of
OL,12,Finterests after he was elected.
OL,14,FUnder the rules in place at the time,
OL,15,Fnew MPs were required to register any
OL,16,Fgifts worth more than #300 they
OL,17,Freceived in the previous 12 months,
OL,18,Fexcept where the gift "could not be
OL,19,Freasonably thought by others" to
OL,20,Frelate to their political activities.
OL,26,@zD@WOU{D@]O]
