OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1782240488
OL,3,CFarage defends #5 million gift saying
OL,4,C'no one cares', as investigation
OL,5,Ccontinues
OL,7,FThe rules also required MPs to bear in
OL,8,Fmind the purpose of the register of
OL,9,Finterests to provide information about
OL,10,Ffinancial interests "which might
OL,11,Freasonably be thought by others to
OL,12,Finfluence his or her actions".
OL,14,FIf found to have breached the rules,
OL,15,FFarage could face sanctions including
OL,16,Fa Commons suspension that could
OL,17,Ftrigger a recall petition and a by-
OL,18,Felection in his seat.
OL,26,@rD@UOUtD@]O]
